    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145780/extras/baf7714c851c13040b8841e994e7d445.poster.avif?t=1754308263\" width=616 height=56 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145780/extras/baf7714c851c13040b8841e994e7d445.webm?t=1754308263\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145780/extras/baf7714c851c13040b8841e994e7d445.mp4?t=1754308263\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Step into the eerie world of '[ANOMALY TAPES]: Beyond Reality,' a retro analog horror game that takes you on a spine-chilling journey through a series of events. Each tape you find brings you closer to uncovering a dark secret, but beware—the anomalies are always lurking.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145780/extras/4b6794bd1af3c418b8ad848d6ce66f1e.poster.avif?t=1754308263\" width=617 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145780/extras/4b6794bd1af3c418b8ad848d6ce66f1e.webm?t=1754308263\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145780/extras/eabed96bf90ce2f28c758fb40b913306.poster.avif?t=1754308263\" width=616 height=56 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145780/extras/eabed96bf90ce2f28c758fb40b913306.webm?t=1754308263\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145780/extras/eabed96bf90ce2f28c758fb40b913306.mp4?t=1754308263\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Explore:</strong> Navigate through 8 main levels, each filled with unique challenges and atmospheric horror.<br></li><li><strong>Survive:</strong> Use a handheld camera perspective to document your journey and avoid deadly anomalies that stalk you relentlessly.<br></li><li><strong>Adapt:</strong> Each entity you encounter has unique gameplay mechanics. Learn and adapt quickly to survive the different challenges posed by each entity.<br></li><li><strong>Discover:</strong> Piece together the story behind the anomalies and your connection to them. Not everything is as it seems.<br></li><li><strong>Analyze:</strong> Replay the game to uncover subtle clues and hidden details that reveal the truth behind this place.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145780/extras/e74644767057ec9a4248f63511b3ed6a.poster.avif?t=1754308263\" width=617 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145780/extras/e74644767057ec9a4248f63511b3ed6a.webm?t=1754308263\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145780/extras/5df270b11e29a25147ef1f12ddbca16e.poster.avif?t=1754308263\" width=616 height=56 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145780/extras/5df270b11e29a25147ef1f12ddbca16e.webm?t=1754308263\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145780/extras/5df270b11e29a25147ef1f12ddbca16e.mp4?t=1754308263\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>In a world where reality bends and twists, you are thrust into something sinister. As you navigate a series of haunting environments, each more disturbing than the last, document your journey along the way. But be careful—each step forward brings you closer to a terrifying revelation.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145780/extras/ab3095b97668d91889d103c686bb42db.poster.avif?t=1754308263\" width=617 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145780/extras/ab3095b97668d91889d103c686bb42db.webm?t=1754308263\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145780/extras/bebfecd7d7d542ebc7df6aa00ba90e04.poster.avif?t=1754308263\" width=616 height=56 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145780/extras/bebfecd7d7d542ebc7df6aa00ba90e04.webm?t=1754308263\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145780/extras/bebfecd7d7d542ebc7df6aa00ba90e04.mp4?t=1754308263\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>As you delve deeper into the mystery, you'll find yourself questioning your own sanity. What dark secrets lie beyond the tapes? '[ANOMALY TAPES]: Beyond Reality' invites you to explore, survive, and uncover the truth—if you dare.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145780/extras/2ce3e9307cf59258e67f6dec494046ad.poster.avif?t=1754308263\" width=617 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145780/extras/2ce3e9307cf59258e67f6dec494046ad.webm?t=1754308263\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
